===My Dux, I am...===
{{Messages|text=
:'''Cerydra:''' My Dux, I am preparing for my first "Extreme Expedition"
:'''Cerydra:''' As one who has journeyed across the stars, you would surely provide more complete advice
:{Choice} Going alone?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Going alone? Where are you headed?
::'''Cerydra:''' If someone wants to come along, I have no objections
:{Choice} Where to?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Where are you headed?
:{Choice} Feel free to board the Astral Express
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Feel free to board the Astral Express
::'''Cerydra:''' A possible stop, perhaps. But not now
:'''Cerydra:''' Amphoreus, in the future
:'''Cerydra:''' On my past conquests, I remember the states only as raging fires of strife or the stagnant, black tide of death
:'''Cerydra:''' When the Seed of Memory blossoms, Amphoreus will burst with life. A perfect time for me to explore it
:'''Cerydra:''' I wish to sail the Skiana seas, where the storm clouds and giant waves are locked in eternal combat
:'''Cerydra:''' Have you heard of Ladon? It's said there's a peak there so high it touches the clouds
:'''Cerydra:''' I'm trying to decide between wingsuit flying and skydiving
:'''Cerydra:''' Any advice, dear Dux?
:{Choice} Either one works
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Either one works. I mean, I do make a habit of spinning, jumping, and dropping into worlds from way up high
::'''Cerydra:''' Excellent proposition
:{Choice} Let's go bungee jumping
::'''(Trailblazer):''' It's a long story... but my usual method of entering a world is by falling into it
::'''(Trailblazer):''' You should give it a go
::'''Cerydra:''' Excellent proposition
:{Choice} Stay safe!
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Please, stay safe!
::'''Cerydra:''' Relax. The Imperator is made of tough stuff
:'''Cerydra:''' I just had wilderness survival training with the little kitten and rope-making class with Dux Goldweaver
:'''Cerydra:''' Now it's time for my swimming lessons with Dux Gladiorum
:'''Cerydra:''' See you later
}}
